{
  "stem": "25027.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were soldiers, and we had a special card with our picture on it and a number where we could get in and out.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's all we could do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a barrack.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Near the factory, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only men.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No social life, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was able to go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When-- when I got the end of the month, I got a couple of rubles, and I was hungry.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I used to go out to the market.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The markets still had Russian peasant women selling from their farms whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, they had their own plots, because most farms were collective farms, so they had their own plots.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they used to make [NON-ENGLISH], they called it, like [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [INAUDIBLE], but they were baked with potato or whatever and they were very expensive.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But whenever it was, I-- I blew my whole month's salary on a couple of these things so I could eat something, [LAUGHS] you know, and survive.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you were there for six months?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Close to-- five-- five and a half months, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then the crops were coming in on the kohlkoz, which is the collective farm.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had no men to take them off, so the men were taken off the factories and sent there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was September sometimes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were sent to take off the food from the collective farms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Still in the army.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Still the same thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Paid.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- but instead of staying in barracks, we stayed individually with peasant families in their homes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Each soldier or two soldiers were assigned to one family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And besides working so many hours taking off the wheat, they were afraid that the Germans were going to break through, so they put us for hours digging trenches.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
